{"tid":448673,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵番一隻Playstation 既game","createTime":"2017-10-26T12:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T14:32:56.000Z","uid":85280,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e67e9ba55c35058b7f462108d116546290af3b1b","tid":448673,"uid":85280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔記得係PS1 定 PS2。印象中，係控制一架可以變做車既藍色機械人，第一關boss 係一隻戰鬥機(好似係綠色)，同埋有一關係地下水道解迷，唔知點樣整著所有燈先可以開到門。雙人過關時，一部係紅色，另一部係藍色。仲有雙人對戰時，可以係地圖上起唔到既基地，基地會自動出坦克同戰鬥機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴打知係咩game"},{"pid":"851060d7e85de35ace807061384f4976a8210fd7","tid":448673,"uid":85280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1305727462089215e825178218ee3511551527cf","tid":448673,"uid":85280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9e47dc4fc0a58a882d76aeae4b85c9db3165b1","tid":448673,"uid":85543,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"Commando 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗多謝"},{"pid":"34fb9812ed48a5a1b585a9ec6586e0037745ed81","tid":448673,"uid":85280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Commando 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗多謝</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔係依隻"},{"pid":"bcefdce38063d382aee8d239e97c86fbce7936d1","tid":448673,"uid":39369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"我諗我知你講邊隻，應該係ps1，英文game黎<br />\n<br